  <brief_title>Dexamethasone Vs Methylprednisolone for the Treatment of Patients With ARDS Caused by COVID-19</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Outcome of Dexamethasone and Methylprednisolone Treatment for Patients With ARDS Caused by COVID-19</official_title>
